==WTC 17758 – Frostburn (2004)== ''[[Frostburn]]: Mastering the Perils of Ice and Snow'' was published in 2004, and written by [[Wolfgang Baur]], [[James Jacobs (game designer)|James Jacobs]], and [[George Strayton]]. Frostburn is an official supplement for the 3.5 edition of Dungeons and Dragons, and includes new content for cold based climate campaigns. The book contains both new playable races and monsters in addition to expanded rules and campaign ideas regarding; High altitude, arctic, and Cold environments in general.
{{ISBN|0-7869-3657-6}}
