==WTC 9537572 – Fiendish Codex I: Hordes of the Abyss (2006)== ''[[Fiendish Codex I: Hordes of the Abyss]]'' was published in 2006, and was written by [[Ed Stark]], [[James Jacobs (game designer)|James Jacobs]], and [[Erik Mona]]. Fiendish Codex I is an official supplement for the 3.5 edition of Dungeons and Dragons, and includes new content for [[Demon (Dungeons & Dragons)|demons]] and inhabitants of the [[Abyss (Dungeons & Dragons)|Abyss]]. Chapter 2 contains statistics for new monsters, on pages 27–56, while Chapter 3 contains statistics for 14 [[Demon lord (Dungeons & Dragons)|demon lords]], on pages 57–80.
{{ISBN|0-7869-3919-2}}
