977)|Monster Manual]], Book of Vile Darkness |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Kostchtchie]] |PageNumber=68–69 |OtherAppearances=[[List of Dungeons & Dragons 1st edition monsters#TSR 2016 - Monster Manual II (1983)|Monster Manual II]] |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Malcanthet]] |PageNumber=69–71 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Obox-ob]] |PageNumber=71–73 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Orcus (Dungeons & Dragons)|Orcus]] |PageNumber=73–74 |OtherAppearances=[[List of Dungeons & Dragons monsters (1974-1976)#TSR 2005 - Dungeons & Dragons Supplement III: Eldritch Wizardry (1976)|Eldritch Wizardry]], [[List of Dungeons & Dragons 1st edition monsters#TSR 2009 - Monster Manual (1977)|Monster Manual]], Book of Vile Darkness |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Pale Night]] |PageNumber=74–76 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Pazuzu (Dungeons & Dragons)|Pazuzu]] |PageNumber=76–77 |OtherAppearances=[[List of Dungeons & Dragons 1st edition monsters#TSR 2016 - Monster Manual II (1983)|Monster Manual II]] |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Yeenoghu]] |PageNumber=78–79 |OtherAppearances=[[List of Dungeons & Dragons 1st edition monsters#TSR 2009 - Monster Manual (1977)|Monster Manual]], Book of Vile Darkness |Variants= |Description= }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Zuggtmoy]] |PageNumber=79–80 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description= }} |}
